  "description": "A wide shot capturing a vibrant meadow teeming with wildflowers under a cloudy sky. The meadow is a mix of green grasses and an array of small, colorful blossoms in shades of white, purple, and pink. A single bird, silhouetted against the sky, is in mid-flight, adding a dynamic element to the serene scene. The sky is overcast with soft, grey clouds creating a diffused light. The horizon line is relatively flat, emphasizing the expansive nature of the meadow.",
